267
00:23:08,726 --> 00:23:11,395
- Anak itu, Mario, dia akan ceritakan.
- Halo.

268
00:23:11,479 --> 00:23:13,772
Bagai mimpi buruk!

269
00:23:15,191 --> 00:23:17,068
Sejak beberapa minggu lalu,

270
00:23:17,151 --> 00:23:20,404
